<header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="label">Bankruptcy Court Index</div>
        <h1>United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of Indiana</h1>
        <p>United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of Indiana is one of the US federal bankruptcy courts whose public, RECAP-archived dockets are indexed here. The Open Bankruptcy Project maintains this national case-level index for empirical research and public-records access. Every case below links to the full docket on the Free Law Project&#x27;s CourtListener.</p>
    </div>
</header>
<main class="container">
    <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-cell"><span class="stat-number green">75,500</span><span class="stat-label">Cases Indexed</span></div>
        <div class="stat-cell"><span class="stat-number accent">151</span><span class="stat-label">Catalog Pages</span></div>
        <div class="stat-cell"><span class="stat-number gold">$0</span><span class="stat-label">Cost to Access</span></div>
    </div>
    
    <section class="section">
        <div class="label" style="font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;">Filing Breakdown</div>
        <h2>Cases by Chapter</h2>
        <p>Distribution of cases in this district by bankruptcy chapter. Source: CourtListener docket metadata. Cases with no chapter value on the docket record are grouped as "Other / Unspecified".</p>
        <div class="chapter-grid">
